TITLE: Defining createChange Function in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the createChange function, which creates a change in the database. It takes arguments for authors, entityId, fileId, lix, pluginKey, schemaKey, snapshotContent, and version. An optional parameter for updating version changes is also included.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opral/monorepo/blob/main/packages/lix-sdk/api-docs/functions/createChange.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
