TITLE: Using Paraglide Messages in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to import and use Paraglide message functions, including passing parameters, changing locales, and retrieving the current locale.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opral/monorepo/blob/main/inlang/packages/paraglide/paraglide-js/docs/getting-started/vanilla-js-ts.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
