LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
select "id", (
  select coalesce(json_group_array(json_object(
    'pet_id', "agg"."pet_id",
    'name', "agg"."name"
  )), '[]') from (
    select "pet"."id" as "pet_id", "pet"."name"
    from "pet"
    where "pet"."owner_id" = "person"."id"
    order by "pet"."name"
  ) as "agg"
) as "pets"
from "person"
```

