TITLE: Generated SQL for jsonObjectFrom() Query in SQLite
DESCRIPTION: Shows the SQL query generated by Kysely when using the jsonObjectFrom() function to fetch a person's favorite pet as a JSON object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opral/monorepo/blob/main/packages/lix-sdk/api-docs/functions/jsonObjectFrom.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
select "id", (
  select json_object(
    'pet_id', "obj"."pet_id",
    'name', "obj"."name"
  ) from (
    select "pet"."id" as "pet_id", "pet"."name"
    from "pet"
    where "pet"."owner_id" = "person"."id"
    and "pet"."is_favorite" = ?
  ) as obj
) as "favorite_pet"
from "person";
```

