TITLE: Working with Unpacked Inlang Files in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to load and save unpacked Inlang files (directories) using TypeScript. It demonstrates using specific functions for directory-based operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opral/monorepo/blob/main/inlang/packages/sdk/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { 
    loadProjectFromDirectory, 
    saveProjectToDirectory 
} from "@inlang/sdk";

const project = await loadProjectFromDirectory({
    "path": "./project.inlang"
});

// modify the project

await saveProjectToDirectory({
