TITLE: Creating Translation Process Flowchart using Mermaid
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid flowchart illustrates the translation process, showing the interaction between developers and translators, and the pipeline for creating, reviewing, approving, and maintaining translations. It includes subgraphs for Developers, Translators, and a Legend explaining the automation levels.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opral/monorepo/blob/main/inlang/assets/graphs.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: mermaid
CODE:
```
flowchart LR
    TF1<--->|hand off|TF2
    subgraph Translators
        direction LR
        TF2[Translation Files]<-->Pipeline
        subgraph Pipeline
            direction TB
            create-->review
            review-->approve
            approve-->maintain
            maintain-->review
        end
    end
    subgraph Developers
    TF1[Translation Files]-->|reference|Code
    Code-->|extract|TF1
    end
    subgraph Legend
      direction LR
      start1[ ] --->|fully automatable| stop1[ ]
      style start1 height:0px;
      style stop1 height:0px;
      start2[ ] --->|highly automatable| stop2[ ]
      style start2 height:0px;
      style stop2 height:0px;
    end
    linkStyle 0 stroke:red;
    linkStyle 2 stroke:red;
    linkStyle 3 stroke:orange;
