TITLE: Concurrent Update Test Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Testing concurrent updates between multiple users with scheduled tasks and offline/online state management
SOURCE: https://github.com/opral/monorepo/blob/main/inlang/packages/parrot-figma/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
